achievements.title: Unending Rain
achievements.description: Cast a power card at least five times during a single turn as Downpour Drenches The World.

achievements.title: They Are Closing In
achievements.description: Have at least 8 Beast tokens inside a single land.

achievements.title: Massive Growth
achievements.description: Have at least one Wilds token inside each land of a single board.

achievements.title: And If I Could Bleed - Well, So Could You!
achievements.description: Win a game with a single blight left.

achievements.title: Without A Scratch
achievements.description: Win a game with no blight on any board.

achievements.title: A High Price To Pay
achievements.description: Destroy a board with Cast Down Into The Briny Deep.

achievements.title: One Trick Pony
achievements.description: Win a game with all but a single power card destroyed.

achievements.title: Power Unleashed
achievements.description: Win a game with all your Spirit Tracks fully uncovered.

achievements.title: All That's Left
achievements.description: Win a game with only a single presence per player left on the board.

achievements.title: I've Got This
achievements.description: Have at least defense 3 in every land on your starting board during a single turn.

achievements.title: And They Run Like Chicken...
achievements.description: Generate at least 20 Fear with a single spirit during a single round.

achievements.title: Flash Flood
achievements.description: Drown 6 invader pieces with your powers during a single turn.

achievements.title: Kaiju
achievements.description: Destroy at least 5 cities in a single turn.

achievements.title: Down The Drain
achievements.description: Deal at least 15 damage with your innate power in a single turn as River Surges In Sunlight.

achievements.title: Obey Or Suffer
achievements.description: Deal at least 20 damage with a single power as Thunderspeaker.

achievements.title: Eradication
achievements.description: Destroy all invaders with a single power.
